    <!-- Title in italics, as in amsthm style.           -->
    <!-- Filled, black square as QED, tombstone, Halmos. -->
    <!-- Pushing the tombstone flush-right is a bit      -->
    <!-- ham-handed, but more elegant TeX-isms           -->
